posts.title: 用make创建map字典
posts.text: package main import “fmt” func main() { a := make(map[int]string) a[1] = “suck” a[2] = “gaybar” a[3] = “doorone” for k, v := range a { fmt.Println(“key=”, k, “value=”, v) }}

posts.title: go slice
posts.text: package main import “fmt” func main() { a := […]int{1, 2, 3, 4, 5, 6, 7} s1 := a[0:4] s2 := a[2:4] s3 := a[4:] fmt.Println(s1, s2, s3) }
